Description: Local voice dictation and command launcher
 Wispr-Lite provides fast, local voice dictation using Whisper AI.
 Features include push-to-talk recording, real-time transcription,
 text insertion without focus stealing, and optional command mode
 for voice-activated system commands.
 .
 All processing happens locally with no cloud dependencies.
